text: Ed Sweeney (1888–1947), was an American Major League Baseball player. Ed Sweeney is also the name of: * Ed Sweeney (American football) (1949–2017), American college football head coach * Ed Sweeney (trade unionist) (born 1954), British former trade union leader * Ed Sweeney, inventor of the Aerocar 2000 and Gemini Hummingbird
title: Ed Sweeney (disambiguation)
